Listener adding should work fine

**Which versions of React, and which browser / OS are affected by this issue? Did this work in previous versions of React?**
I tested React 16.3-alpha.1. I think the issue also exists in React 15 - I was able to reproduce the problem locally with React 15 but I had to make some manual tweaks to create-react-context to make it backward compatible (I've now [published a polyfill](https://github.com/benwiley4000/react-dot-fragment) to make this sort of thing easier).
